Class EBinList

java.lang.Object
  erjang.EObject
      erjang.ECons
          erjang.EBinList

public class EBinList
extends ECons

Special cons cell optimizing for [byte, byte, byte | Tail]. An EBinList has a tail, and an array of bytes for the values it contains. It is optimized for the case of cons'ing a byte onto it; it works like a java StringBuilder, but its contents array grows backwards; so the bytes contained in it are stored in the last bytes of the data array variable.
